{"tid":1767233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成立一個義士職業介紹中心","createTime":"2019-12-03T07:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T08:10:29.000Z","uid":328061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"032abca5b7ed1032c6db20b9037d963db2d07bc0","tid":1767233,"uid":328061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T07:17:50.000Z","msg":"我突然間有個想法，有好多義士失咗業<br />\n我想幫佢哋<span style=\"color: orange;\">搵返一份更好嘅工作</span><br />\n我想成立一個義士職業介紹中心( <span style=\"color: orange;\">初期只係一個網站</span>)<br />\n有黃店老闆唔想請<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍絲</span><br />\n有義士又唔想入咗一間 <span style=\"color: blue;\">藍色企業</span>度做嘢<br />\n希望有一日<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你嘅同事甚至你嘅老闆</span></span>都係支持民主自由 五大訴求缺一不可嘅人<br />\n各位大佬覺得好行嗎？"},{"pid":"8df144403bb64e991d1f756a941f6cfbe7aad3dd","tid":1767233,"uid":335391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T07:23:48.000Z","msg":"搵非建制區域議員。佢哋有budget"},{"pid":"5f10d8f38bc27ab0c3c3416c89843cf8766596e6","tid":1767233,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T07:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103b38e0d36c9d9d6d7328692b71cfb476921b3d","tid":1767233,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T07:36:04.000Z","msg":"已經有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b40ce8704944fdba7f56abfc6ff190834942d3","tid":1767233,"uid":328061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"103b38e0d36c9d9d6d7328692b71cfb476921b3d","tid":1767233,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T07:36:04.000Z","msg":"已經有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T08:03:50.000Z","msg":"已經有咩？ 我未驚過喎"},{"pid":"2d03a7bbf70edee1893b652f3aa486e58b70af32","tid":1767233,"uid":328061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43b40ce8704944fdba7f56abfc6